official_title: To authorize a Wall of Remembrance as part of the Korean War Veterans Memorial and to allow certain private contributions to fund that Wall of Remembrance.
short_title: Korean War Veterans Memorial Wall of Remembrance Act of 2015

summary.text:
Korean War Veterans Memorial Wall of Remembrance Act of 2015

(Sec. 2) This bill authorizes a Wall of Remembrance, as part of the previously authorized Korean War Veterans Memorial, to include:

 a list by name of members of the Armed Forces who died in theatre in the Korean War; the number of members who were wounded, listed as missing in action, or prisoners of war; and the number of members of the Korean Augmentation to the U.S. Army, the Republic of Korea Armed Forces, and the other nations of the United Nations Command who were killed, wounded, missing, or prisoners. The bill prohibits using any federal funds to construct the Wall.
